e%20CBP%20owes%20%24165%20billion%20in%20duties%20that%20must%20be%20refunded%20with%20interest%2C%20with%20about%20%24650%20million%20accruing%20each%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Trump%20introduced%20a%20new%2010%25%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20tariff%26quot%3B%20under%20Section%20122%2C%20meaning%20that%20overseas%20purchases%20will%20continue%20to%20face%20an%20extra%20charge%2C%20some%20shipping%20companies%20told%20Business%20Insider%20they%20are%20willing%20to%20help%20consumers%20claw%20back%20what%20they%20paid%20under%20the%20IEEPA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20FedEx%20to%20USPS%2C%20here%20is%20what%20different%20companies%20are%20saying%20about%20refunding%20tariffs%20paid%20by%20individual%20consumers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d341600e-a40f-4d78-a552-4424262b3781%5C%22%3ESome%20companies%20are%20willing%20to%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFedEx%20was%20the%20first%20company%20to%20file%20a%20lawsuit%20with%20the%20CIT%20to%20secure%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthere-top-global-companies-have-sued-trump-for-tariff-refunds-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ea%20full%20refund%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20after%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20spokesperson%20for%20FedEx%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20lawsuit%20was%20%26quot%3Bon%20behalf%20of%20our%20customers%26quot%3B%20and%20that%20the%20company%20is%20committed%20to%20returning%20tariff%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20intent%20is%20straightforward%3A%20if%20refunds%20are%20issued%20to%20FedEx%2C%20we%20will%20issue%20refunds%20to%20the%20shippers%20and%20consumers%20who%20originally%20bore%20those%20charges%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20that%20will%20happen%2C%20and%20the%20exact%20process%20for%20requesting%20and%20issuing%20refunds%20will%20depend%20in%20part%20on%20future%20guidance%20from%20the%20government%20and%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilar%20to%20FedEx%2C%20UPS%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20company%20will%20support%20customers%20in%20obtaining%20IEEPA%20tariff%20refunds%20after%20a%20process%20is%20established%20by%20relevant%20agencies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20remain%20focused%20on%20keeping%20shipments%20moving%20and%20helping%20ensure%20our%20customers%20can%20fully%20exercise%20their%20rights%20throughout%20this%20complex%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20UPS%20spokesperson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMorgan%20%26amp%3B%20Morgan%20also%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efiled%20a%20proposed%20class%20action%20lawsuit%20in%20March%20against%20FedEx%20to%20recover%20the%20costs%20of%20import%20duties%20and%20fees%20associated%20with%20IEEPA%20in%20a%20legally%20binding%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20FedEx%20has%20stated%20publicly%20that%20they%20plan%20to%20return%20those%20funds%20to%20their%20customers%2C%20the%20company%20did%20not%20make%20any%20legally%20binding%20statements%20to%20that%20effect%20in%20their%20complaint%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Morgan%20%26amp%3B%20Morgan%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20%26quot%3BNor%20have%20they%20mentioned%20any%20plan%20to%20refund%20the%20significant%20ancillary%20fees%20they%20charged%20for%20processing%20those%20tariffs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2282426521-a2bc-4220-8430-ab7cff88e2bc%5C%22%3EOther%20major%20companies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUSPS%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20popular%20and%20affordable%20methods%20of%20shipping%20small%20goods%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20complicated%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivatizing-usps-impact-on-business-nonprofits-rural-areas-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egovernment-owned%20entity%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUSPS%20has%20been%20collecting%20tariffs%20for%20items%20via%20its%20prepaid%20%26quot%3BDelivered%20Duty%20Paid%26quot%3B%20service%2C%20mostly%20to%20avoid%20surprise%20fees%20and%20a%20buildup%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-tariff-de-minimis-postal-suspension-small-business-impact-solutions-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eabandoned%20small%20items%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20border.%20Unlike%20FedEx%20or%20UPS%2C%20it%20is%20an%20independent%20agency%20that%20belongs%20to%20the%20executive%20branch%20of%20the%20federal%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20USPS%20pays%20for%20its%20own%20operations%20and%20is%20not%20funded%20by%20taxpayers%2C%20it%20is%20legally%20complicated%20for%20federal%20agencies%20to%20sue%20each%20other%20in%20court%20because%20they%20are%20part%20of%20the%20same%20legal%20entity%2C%20so%20it%20is%20unknown%20if%20USPS%20could%20obtain%20refunds%20for%20shippers%20or%20receivers%20through%20legal%20means.%20According%20to%20the%20Department%20of%20Justice%20website%2C%20a%20government%20agency%20can%20sue%20another%20only%20if%20it%20can%20prove%20a%20concrete%20adversity%20of%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20USPS%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20CBP%20is%20responsible%20for%20questions%20regarding%20the%20%26quot%3Bdisposition%20of%20tariff%20monies.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CBP%20and%20shipping%20company%20DHL%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-shipping-companies-are-saying-about-ieepa-tariff-refunds-fedex-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773741721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b34c18a7a4f9df67ba45b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-shipping-companies-are-saying-about-ieepa-tariff-refunds-fedex-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22If%20you%20bought%20something%20overseas%20that%20required%20shipping%20last%20year%2C%20some%20shipping%20companies%20are%20willing%20to%20help%20claw%20back%2