t%3Beasy%20to%20fit%20alongside%20auditions%2C%20classes%2C%20or%20rehearsals%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20improvise%20scenes%2C%20explore%20characters%2C%20and%20respond%20naturally%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20with%20plenty%20of%20creative%20freedom%20to%20shape%20how%20each%20interaction%20unfolds%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fjoinhandshake.com%2Fai%2Fopportunities%2Fimprov-actor-ai-trainer%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejob%20listing%3C%2Fa%3E%20reads.%20Embedded%20in%20the%20job%20description%20is%20a%20video%20of%20two%20people%20talking%20in%20an%20apparently%20improvised%20scene.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20listing%20says%20the%20project%20is%20for%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20leading%20AI%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20it%20doesn't%20mention%20how%20the%20work%20will%20be%20used.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Handshake%20spokesperson%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20the%20company%20launched%20an%20AI%20division%20after%20about%20a%20decade%20as%20a%20social%20network%20for%20college%20students%20and%20young%20professionals%20looking%20for%20career%20opportunities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Reddit%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2Fai-artificial-intelligence%2F893931%2Fai-companies-handshake-improv-actors-training-data%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Verge%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20users%20debated%20what%20Handshake's%20plans%20for%20the%20recordings%20might%20be.%20One%20user%20posted%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20clearly%20just%20an%20attempt%20to%20get%20people%20to%20train%20AI%20models%20to%20create%20AI%20generated%20videos.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20predicted%20that%20it%20could%20lead%20to%20more%20demand%20for%20%26quot%3Breal%2C%20unpolished%26quot%3B%20live%20comedy%20from%20humans%2C%20even%20if%20the%20work%20is%20used%20to%20create%20AI%20that%20can%20generate%20comedy.%3