e%20credit%2C%20and%20AI%20fears%20are%20some%20of%20the%20key%20stressors%20he%20flagged.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ERisks%20of%20a%20financial%20crisis%20are%20brewing%2C%20and%20it%20could%20be%20worse%20than%20the%20Great%20Recession%2C%20according%20to%20a%20longtime%20finance%20pro%20who%20predicted%20the%202008%20crisis.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Bookstaber%2C%20a%20Wall%20Street%20veteran%20who%20wrote%20a%202007%20book%20that%20foreshadowed%20the%20Great%20Recession%2C%20said%20there%20are%20compounding%20stressors%20in%20the%20financial%20market%20that%20are%20not%20only%20reminiscent%20of%20the%20Great%20Recession%20but%20suggest%20the%20next%20crisis%20could%20be%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBookstaber%20is%20familiar%20with%20financial%20crises%2C%20having%20spent%20decades%20working%20in%20risk%20management%20at%20companies%20like%20Morgan%20Stanley%20and%20Bridgewater%2C%20as%20well%20as%20at%20the%20US%20Treasury%20and%20the%20Securities%20and%20Exchange%20Commission%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202008%20housing%20crisis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20returned%20to%20a%20period%20of%20risk%2C%20one%20rife%20with%20the%20sort%20of%20pressures%20that%20have%20led%20to%20major%20financial%20crises%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20expert%20wrote%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2026%2F03%2F16%2Fopinion%2Ffinancial-crisis-private-credit-ai-iran-taiwan.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Times%20op-ed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20explaining%20that%20he%20went%20from%20telling%20his%20younger%20colleagues%20that%20they'll%20never%20see%20anything%20like%20the%202008%20recession%20again%2C%20to%20worrying%20the%20next%20crisis%20could%20be%20more%20damaging.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20outlined%20four%20distinct%20but%20interconnected%20stressors%20threatening%20the%20financial%20system.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22618dd4ac-55e6-48ec-b655-81f14dbf96d9%5C%22%3EStress%20in%20private%20credit%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-financial-crisis-blackrock-blue-owl-debt-software-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPrivate%20credit%3C%2Fa%3E%20fears%20have%20ramped%20up%20in%20recent%20months%20after%20asset%20managers%2C%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-crisis-blue-owl-wall-street-owl-stock-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlue%20Owl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20BlackRock%2C%20Blackstone%2C%20and%20Morgan%20Stanley%20limited%20redemptions%20for%20some%20funds.%20The%20restrictions%20sparked%20fears%20about%20liquidity%20and%20a%20panic%20in%20the%20sector%20as%20investors%20rush%20for%20the%20exits.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBookstaber%20said%20companies%20have%20become%20increasingly%20reliant%20on%20institutional%20lenders%20since%20the%20financial%20crisis.%20%26quot%3BThese%20loans%20rarely%20exchange%20hands%2C%20leaving%20investors%20uncertain%20about%20what%20these%20instruments%20are%20really%20worth%20or%20how%20easily%20they%20could%20be%20sold%20if%20conditions%20deteriorate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFamed%20investor%20Mohamed%20El-Erian%20said%20private%20credit%20redemption%20freezes%20could%20be%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-financial-crisis-risk-gfc-blue-owl-withdrawals-frozen-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%26quot%3Bcanary-in-the-coalmine%26quot%3B%20moment%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20similar%20to%20the%20run-up%20to%202008.%20George%20Noble%2C%20a%20longtime%20Fidelity%20fund%20manager%2C%20also%20warned%20that%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprivate-credit-financial-crisis-blackrock-blue-owl-debt-software-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ewe're%20watching%20a%20financial%20crisis%20unfold%20in%20real%20time%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2207357cdd-c292-4f31-b