5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b46caca96e437d6eb84e79%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223490%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHanko%20Kiessner%20put%20EV%20chargers%20in%20his%20company's%20parking%20lot.%3Cp%3EHansi%20Kiessner%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPacksize%20founder%20Hanko%20Kiessner%20became%20a%20proponent%20of%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fev-owners-victory-lap-gas-prices-skyrocket-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelectric%20vehicles%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20developing%20asthma.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20installed%20chargers%20in%20his%20company's%20parking%20lot%20several%20years%20ago%20to%20help%20reduce%20air%20pollution.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EKiessner%20says%20they're%20a%20low-cost%20perk%20that%20can%20help%20attract%20and%20retain%20talent%2C%20especially%20when%20gas%20prices%20soar.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fhanko-kiessner-9831388%2Foverlay%2Fabout-this-profile%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHanko%20Kiessner%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20founder%20and%20vice%20chairman%20of%20Packsize%2C%20a%20Salt%20Lake%20City-based%20packaging%20company.%20This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20just%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-price-hits-100-what-smart-people-are-saying-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Espike%20in%20gas%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20everyone%20is%20complaining.%20I%20see%20an%20affordable%20solution%20for%20employers%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that%20could%20also%20grow%20worker%20loyalty%3A%20adding%20EV%20charging%20stations%20to%20their%20parking%20lots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20something%20I%20discovered%20after%20moving%20in%202002%20from%20Germany%2C%20where%20I%20grew%20up%2C%20to%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20and%20starting%20Packsize.%20I%20didn't%20know%20about%20the%20air%20pollution%20problem%20here%2C%20and%20after%20a%20few%20years.%20I%20developed%20asthma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20never%20had%20this%20problem%20before.%20I'm%20very%20active.%20I%20run%20marathons.%20So%20I%20did%20research%20to%20find%20out%20what%20was%20causing%20my%20asthma%20and%20concluded%20that%20air%20pollution%20was%20to%20blame.%20I%20also%20learned%20that%20air%20pollution%20largely%20comes%20from%20vehicles%20and%20can%20cause%20inflammation%20in%20the%20lungs%2C%20which%20can%20lead%20to%20cancer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAround%20this%20time%2C%20electric%20cars%20were%20becoming%20popular.%20I%20learned%20so%20much%20about%20this%20disruptive%20technology%20that%20I%20started%20a%20nonprofit%20called%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.leadersforcleanair.org%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELeaders%20for%20Clean%20Air%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20several%20other%20local%20entrepreneurs.%20Our%20mission%20is%20to%20raise%20money%20to%20buy%20EV%20charging%20stations%20and%20have%20them%20installed%20in%20as%20many%20places%20as%20possible.%20We%20see%20this%20as%20a%20business%20matter.%20We%20need%20to%20attract%20talent%20from%20other%20markets%20to%20grow%2C%20and%20air%20pollution%20hinders%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20wanted%20to%20motivate%20more%20people%20than%20just%20me%20to%20drive%20an%20electric%20car%2C%20so%20I%20asked%20my%20employees%3A%20What%20prevents%20you%20from%20buying%20one%3F%20And%20the%20answer%20was%20that%20charging%20stations%20are%20not%20ubiquitous.%20One%20of%20the%20biggest%20fears%20for%20people%20with%20EVs%20is%20driving%20to%20work%20and%20not%20finding%20a%20plug.%20That%20is%20scary%20because%20now%20you%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20make%20it%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20initially%20set%20up%20just%20three%20charging%20stations%20at%20our%20Utah%20headquarters%2C%20where%20we%20have%20about%20100%20employees.%20Then%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20people%20got%20EVs%2C%20so%20we%20added%20more.%20Today%2C%20we%20have%2053%20stations%20and%20are%20close%20to%20a%2030%25%20EV%20adoption%20rate%20among%20staff%2C%20which%20means%20there%20are%20some%20extra%20plugs%20for%20visitors%20and%20employees%20at%20neighboring%20businesses.%20We%20learned%20that%20the%20infrastructure%20has%20to%20come%20first.%20Most%20employees%20switched%20after%20the%20charging%20stations%20were%20installed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20stations%20are%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20cheapest%20benefits%20an%20employer%20can%20offer%20their%20staff.%20The%20cost%20of%20electricity%20at%20a%20corporate%20rate%20is%20low%20%E2%80%94%20for%20us%2C%20it's%20about%20%243%20a%20day%20per%20charging%20station.%20In%20today's%20post-COVID%20world%2C%20it's%20also%20a%20way%20to%20get%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigher-gas-prices-affect-commute-rto-debate-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eback%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20really%20cool%20thing%3A%20I'm%20now%20attracting%20employees%20who%20drive%20EVs%2C%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethey're%20very%20desirable.%20They%20typically%20care%20about%20the%20environment%20and%20understand%20that%20EV%20driving%20is%20cheaper%20than%20gasoline%20driving.%20They%20also%20tend%20to%20be%20tech-savvy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20gas%20prices%20are%20so%20high%2C%20more%20people%20may%20consider%20buying%20EVs.%20Oil%20supply%20chains%20are%20fragile%2C%20and%20we%20have%20an%20abundance%20of%20cheap%20electricity.%20For%20employers%2C%20helping%20workers%20make%20that%20switch%20can%20be%20as%20simple%20as%20putting%20charging%20stations%20in%20their%20parking%20lots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffounder-says-ev-chargers-are-key-employee-perk-gas-costs-2026-3%5C%