inment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fcheap-tactics-attention-seeking-ke-liye-hadd-paar-kardi-hai-kangana-ranaut-reacts-to-nora-fatehi-sanjay-dutts-song-sarke-chunar%2Farticleshow%2F129628885.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22R.%20Parthiban%20issues%20apology%20over%20%E2%80%98Ustaad%20Bhagat%20Singh%E2%80%99%20event%20row%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773739854000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129628809%2Cimgsize-276760.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Ftamil%2Fmovies%2Fnews%2Fr-parthiban-issues-apology-over-ustaad-bhagat-singh-event-row-says-he-was-tensed-and-struggled-with-telugu%2Farticleshow%2F129628809.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129628809.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFilmmaker%20R.%20Parthiban%20has%20apologized%20for%20a%20caste-related%20remark%20made%20at%20the%20'Ustaad%20Bhagat%20Singh'%20event%2C%20explaining%20he%20felt%20tense%20and%20struggled%20with%20Telugu.%20He%20clarified%20that%20while%20his%20origins%20are%20different%2C%20his%20life%20and%20career%20are%20tied%20to%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20he%20regrets%20any%20hurt%20caused%20by%20his%20attempt%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20Telugu%20audience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20top%202%25%20fund%20manager%20shares%20the%203%20most%20AI-proof%20stocks%20he's%20betting%20on%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22wall%20street%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b832d3a96e437d6eb8604e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESpencer%20Platt%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETom%20Hancock%20of%20GMO%20shared%20three%20stocks%20he%20thinks%20are%20insulated%20from%20AI%20disruption.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHis%20picks%20include%20software%20makers%20SAP%20and%20Jack%20Henry.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHancock's%20GMO%20Quality%20Fund%20has%20beaten%2098%25%20of%20similar%20funds%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Iran%20war%20and%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-climb-iran-war-gas-trump-us-israel-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espike%20in%20oil%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%20can%20make%20it%20easy%20to%20forget%20that%20just%20weeks%20ago%2C%20markets%20were%20in%20a%20panic%20about%20AI%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20threat%20is%20still%20in%20the%20background%2C%20and%20one%20fund%20manager%20has%20a%20trio%20of%20stock%20picks%20to%20consider%20whenever%20the%20market%20starts%20fretting%20over%20AI%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTwo%20years%20ago%2C%20people%20would%20say%20software%20is%20the%20best%20business%20model%20in%20the%20world%2C%20and%20now%20all%20of%20a%20sudden%2C%20people%20start%20talking%20about%20terminal%20value%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvesting-stock-market-strategy-iran-war-oil-prices-surging-gmo-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETom%20Hancock%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20head%20of%20the%20Focused%20Equity%20team%20at%20asset%20management%20firm%20GMO%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20were%20a%20jab%20at%20what%20he%20thinks%20turned%20into%20a%20panic-selling%20episode%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20this%20year%2C%20but%20there's%20some%20truth%20in%20the%20idea%20that%20business%20models%20and%20valuations%20are%20in%20flux.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20many%20fund%20managers%2C%20Hancock%20says%20he's%20recently%20had%20to%20reevaluate%20the%20companies%20he%20invests%20in%20amid%20fears%20of%20AI%20disruption.%20Hancock%20runs%20a%20few%20funds%20%E2%80%94%20the%20GMO%20Quality%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Fgmo-quality-fund-class-iii-us3620082608%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGQETX%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20the%20US%20Quality%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fgmo-us-quality-etf-us90139k1007%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EQLTY%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20and%20the%20recently%20launched%20GMO%20Domestic%20Resilience%20ETF%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fetfs%2Fgmo-domestic-resilience-etf-us90139k8606%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDRES%3C%2Fa%3E).%20He's%20overseen%20the%20GMO%20Quality%20Fund%20since%202004%2C%20and%20over%20the%20last%2015%20years%2C%20he's%20beaten%2098%25%20of%20similar%20funds%20by%20returning%20an%20average%20of%20over%2014%25%20a%20year%2C%20according%20to%20Morningstar%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20quality-factor%20funds%20are%20overweight%20technology%20firms%20relative%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20That%20means%20Hancock%20has%20significant%20exposure%20to%20firms%20vulnerable%20to%20the%20AI%20disruption%20theme%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20software%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20he%20tries%20to%20avoid%20the%20threat%20by%20going%20through%20a%20checklist%20of%20characteristics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20in%20software%20companies%20is%20ones%20where%2C%20if%20you%20spin%20up%20an%20AI%20substitute%2C%20people%20aren't%20going%20to%20be%20inclined%20to%20use%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BLet's%20say%20a%20software%20company%20has%20some%20sort%20of%20regulatory%20lock-in%20or%20proprietary%20data%20built%20into%20it.%20Switching%20costs%20are%20very%20high%2C%20and%20there's%20sort%20of%20a%20network%20effect%20or%20an%20ecosystem%20around%20people%20using%20it.%20Various%20characteristics%20like%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHancock%20shared%20three%20examples%20of%20companies%20he%20invests%20in%20that%20he%20sees%20as%20particularly%20resilient%20to%20AI%20disruption.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a0a428fc-9e6f-469a-b551-1c7890dbb8f2%5C%22%3E3%20AI-resilient%20stocks%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20is%20German%20enterprise%20software%20firm%20%3Cstrong%3ESAP%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fsap-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ESAP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20which%20trades%20in%20the%20US%20on%20the%20New%20York%20Stock%20Exchange.%20Hancock%20pointed%20to%20enterprise%20resource%20planning%20tools%20specifically%2C%20which%20coordinate%20key%20business%20functions%20from%20accounting%20to%20supply%20chains.%20Executives%20don't%20yet%20trust%20AI%20enough%20to%20outsource%20their%20logistics%20needs%20to%20it%2C%20Hancock%20said%2C%20and%20with%20changing%20tariff%20rates%2C%20logistics%20are%20too%20complex%20not%20to%20use%20an%20established%2C%20credible%20provider%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGetting%20your%20logistics%20wrong%2C%20the%20costs%20of%20that%20are%20so%20high.%20There's%20so%20much%20expertise%2C%26quot%3B%20Hancock%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20not%20going%20to%20start%20using%20the%20ERP%20system%20that%20someone%20vibecoded%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHancock%20described%20shares%20of%20SAP%20as%20the%20best%20individual-stock%20opportunity%20he%20sees%20right%20now%2C%20as%20fears%20of%20AI%20disruption%20in%20the%20software%20space%20are%20overdone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20Hancock%20said%20%3Cstrong%3EConstellation%20Software%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fcnswf-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECNSWF%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20fairly%20insulated%20from%20AI.%20While%20the%20products%20aren't%20extremely%20high-tech%2C%20he%20said%2C%20their%20customers%20value%20the%20simplicity.%20The%20firm%20has%20clients%20in%20local%20governments%2C%20education%2C%20healthcare%2C%20the%20restaurant%20industry%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20customers%20want%20something%2C%20they%20come%20to%20the%20vendors%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20almost%20like%20a%20consultant-type%20relationship%20there%20that%20an%20AI%20solution%20couldn't%20provide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThird%2C%20Hancock%20flagged%20%3Cstrong%3EJack%20Henry%20(%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fjkhy-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EJKHY%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cstrong%3E)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20a%20company%20that%20makes%20payments%20and%20processing%20software%20for%20banks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20technical%20expertise%20that%20is%20hard%20to%20replicate%2C%20high%20costs%20to%20making%20mistakes%2C%20a%20hurdle%20in%20retraining%20users%2C%20and%20regulatory%20issues%20than%20make%20switching%20risky%2C%26quot%3B%20Hancock%20said.%20%26quot%3BAs%20a%20bonus%2C%20their%20pricing%20is%20more%20based%20on%20transactions%20than%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-proof-stock-picks-to-buy-top-fund-manager-gmo-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773739801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b832e54d65ec51752a122b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-proof-stock-picks-to-buy-top-fund-manager-gmo-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Iran%20war%20has%20overshadowed%20this%20year's%20AI%20panic%2C%20but%20the%20risk%20is%20still%20lurking.%20Here's%20a%20fund