-issues-notice-mere-khwabon-mein-towel-dance-ddlj-west-bengal-nhrc-11227143%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20video%2C%20which%20is%20doing%20rounds%20on%20social%20media%2C%20shows%20two%20girls%20dancing%20to%20the%20song%20'Mere%20Khwabon%20Mein'%20from%20the%20film%20'Dilwale%20Dulhaniya%20Le%20Jayenge'%20at%20a%20cultural%20event%20in%20the%20school.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftowel-dance-at-bengal-school-sparks-row-rights-body-issues-notice-mere-khwabon-mein-towel-dance-ddlj-west-bengal-nhrc-11227143%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Marc%20Andreessen%20explains%20why%20he%20won't%20be%20jumping%20on%20Silicon%20Valley's%20ayahuasca%20trend%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Marc%20Andreessen%20is%20sitting%20on%20a%20black%20leather%20chair%20onstage.%20He's%20wearing%20a%20white%20button-up%20shirt%20with%20a%20gray%20window%20pane%20pattern.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b818a4a96e437d6eb85d53%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221996%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMarc%20Andreessen%2C%20one%20of%20Silicon%20Valley's%20most%20outspoken%20executives%2C%20says%20he's%20seen%20top%20bosses%20leave%20their%20companies%20and%20become%20surf%20instructors%20after%20taking%20drugs.%3Cp%3ESteve%20Jennings%2FGetty%20Images%20for%20TechCrunch%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMarc%20Andreessen%20said%20he's%20not%20interested%20in%20taking%20psychedelics%20%E2%80%94%20even%20as%20other%20executives%20recommend%20ayahuasca.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20says%20he's%20seen%20tech%20leaders%20use%20the%20drugs%20and%20%26quot%3Bmove%20to%20Indonesia%20and%20become%20a%20surf%20instructor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EInstead%2C%20Andreessen%20said%20he%20uses%20another%20drug%20that%20once%20made%20his%20heart%20skip%20every%2010th%20beat.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EMarc%20Andreessen%20says%20he's%20heard%20enough%20stories%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpsychedelics-startups-venture-capital-silicon-valley-investors-funding-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epsychedelics%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20know%20they're%20not%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fsi%3D9qo2DdxtpdtZ4Y82%26v%3DqBVe3M2g_SA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDavid%20Senra's%20podcast%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20cofounder%20of%20Andreessen%20Horowitz%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20venture%20capital%20firms%20in%20the%20Bay%20Area%20%E2%80%94%20said%20some%20founders%20who%20experiment%20with%20hallucinogenic%20drugs%20become%20calmer%20and%20more%20at%20peace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20they%20also%20sometimes%20lose%20interest%20in%20running%20their%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20tons%20of%20horror%20stories%20from%20people%20I%20know%20or%20know%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20try%20it%2C%20and%20they%20kind%20of%20come%20out%20the%20other%20end%20as%20a%20changed%20person.%20They%20come%20out%20much%20more%20at%20peace%2C%20but%20then%20they%20also%20tend%20to%20quit%20their%20companies%2C%20and%20they%20move%20to%20Indonesia%20and%20become%20a%20surf%20instructor.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndreessen%20said%20he's%20noticed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-andreessen-elon-musk-playbook-advice-examples-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epattern%20among%20founders%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20turn%20to%20psychedelics%20%E2%80%94%20particularly%20ayahuasca%20%E2%80%94%20while%20under%20intense%20pressure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20he%20once%20discussed%20the%20phenomenon%20with%20Stanford%20University%20neuroscientist%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-dopamine-restricting-for-procrastination-motivation-productivity-strategy-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epodcaster%20Andrew%20Huberman%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Huberman%20suggested%20that%20becoming%20less%20anxious%20might%20actually%20be%20the%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20in%20true%20Huberman%20kind%20of%20wise%20Yoda%20style%2C%20he's%20like%2C%20'Well%2C%20you%20know%2C%20how%20do%20you%20know%20they're%20not%20happier%3F'%26quot%3B%20Andreessen%20said.%20%26quot%3BMaybe%20the%20thing%20that%20was%20driving%20them%20to%20be%20a%20great%20entrepreneur%20was%20a%20fundamental%20level%20of%20insecurity.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstead%2C%20he%20said%20that%20his%20preferred%20drug%20is%20far%20more%20conventional%3A%20caffeine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAndreessen%20said%20he%20once%20had%20so%20many%20cups%20of%20coffee%20that%20his%20heart%20was%20skipping%20every%2010th%20beat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20psychedelics%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20has%20become%20increasingly%20mainstream%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEntrepreneurs%20and%20investors%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceos-founders-who-used-psychedelics-lsd-acid-magic-mushrooms%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Espoken%20openly%20about%20experimenting%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20substances%20like%20LSD%2C%20psilocybin%2C%20or%20ayahuasca%2C%20often%20framing%20them%20as%20tools%20for%20self-discovery%2C%20creativity%2C%20or%20mental%20health.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20hasn't%20convinced%20Andreessen%20to%20try%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20possibility%20that%20there's%20a%20better%20version%20of%20you%20or%20me%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20ayahuasca%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20I'm%20not%20willing%20to%20find%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarc-andreeson-silicon-valley-ayahuasca-trend-202