tal%20and%20artificial%20intelligence%20officer%2C%20said%20during%20a%20presentation%20at%20Palantir's%20AIPCon%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLeft%20click%2C%20right%20click%2C%20left%20click%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalantir%20posted%20a%20video%20of%20Stanley's%20demonstration%20over%20the%20weekend%20showing%20how%20the%20system%20could%20use%20satellite%20imagery%20alongside%20multiple%20data%20feeds%2C%20including%20a%20flight-tracking%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUsing%20the%20system%2C%20he%20highlighted%20how%20the%20list%20of%20potential%20targets%20could%20be%20narrowed%20to%20a%20specific%20car%20in%20the%20parking%20lot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22youtube%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20referrerpolicy%3D%5C%22strict-origin-when-cross-origin%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FyrtDgoqWmgM%3Fstart%3D356%26feature%3Doembed%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Multi-Domain%20AI%3A%20The%20Future%20of%20Command%20and%20Control%20%7C%20CDAO%20at%20AIPCon%209%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22315%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20part%20of%20the%20demo%2C%20Stanley%20showed%20how%20artificial%20intelligence%20is%20used%20to%20identify%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20the%20best%20asset%26quot%3B%20is%20to%20carry%20out%20the%20strike.%20For%20the%20demonstration%2C%20it%20was%20a%20mounted%20.50-caliber%20M2%20Browning%20machine%20gun%20on%20a%20Stryker%20armored%20fighting%20vehicle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe've%20gone%20from%20identifying%20the%20target%2C%20to%20now%20coming%20up%20with%20a%20course%20of%20action%2C%20to%20now%20actioning%20that%20target%20all%20within%20one%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Stanley%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20revolutionary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20having%20this%20done%20in%20about%20eight%20or%20nine%20systems%2C%20where%20humans%20were%20literally%20moving%20detections%20left%20and%20right%20in%20order%20to%20get%20to%20a%20desire%20end%20state%2C%20in%20this%20case%20actually%20closing%20a%20kill%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20pointing%20to%20combat%20footage%20of%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20started%20this%2C%20it%20literally%20took%20hours%20to%20do%20what%20you%20just%20saw%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20the%20process%20of%20going%20from%20detection%20to%20targeting%20to%20decision-making%20to%20engagement.%20%26quot%3BWe've%20been%20able%20to%20reduce%20that%20time%20significantly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPalantir%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falex-karp-bio-palantir-ceo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAlex%20Karp%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20his%20deputies%20are%20somewhat%20cagey%20about%20exactly%20what%20Project%20Maven%20entails%2C%20given%20its%20classified%20uses.%20Citing%20information%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20papers%2C%26quot%3B%20Karp%20said%20that%20his%20company%20has%20provided%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%20an%20advantage%20on%20the%20battlefield.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20fact%20that%20you%20can%20now%20target%20more%20precisely%2C%20more%20accurately%2C%20more%20quickly%2C%20and%20that%2C%20meaning%20America%2C%20can%20do%20all%20these%2C%20organize%20the%20total%20power%20of%20our%20fleet%20and%20all%20of%20our%20resources%2C%20and%20bring%20it%20to%20bear%20against%20our%20adversaries%20and%20enemies%20has%20shifted%20the%20way%20in%20which%20war%20is%20fought%2C%26quot%3B%20Karp%20told%20CNBC%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20conference.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20I%20have%20read%20that%20Palantir's%20Project%20Maven%20is%20the%20core%20backbone%20of%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army's%20Commander%20and%20Staff%20Guide%20to%20Data%20Literacy%20says%20that%20Maven%20is%20part%20of%20%26quot%3Bthe%20cutting-edge%20capabilities%26quot%3B%20troops%20rely%20on%20%26quot%3Bto%20assist%20in%20targeting%20and%20executing%20strikes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20MSS%20can%20greatly%20enable%20the%20decision-making%20process%2C%20staff%20members%20will%20need%20to%20have%20a%20cursory%20understanding%20of%20how%20these%20emerging%20systems%20function%20to%20fully%20appreciate%20their%20capabilities%20and%20limitations%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20guide%20reads%2C%20referring%20to%20the%20Maven%20Smart%20System.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MSS%20has%20been%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20US's%20War%20in%20Iran%2C%20The%20Washington%20Post%20recently%20reported.%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20is%20embedded%20in%20the%20system%2C%20a%20topic%20of%20major%20discussion%20after%20Defense%20Secretary%20Pete%20Hegseth%20moved%20to%20effectively%20blacklist%20the%20AI%20startup%20after%20it%20refused%20to%20give%20the%20Pentagon%20unfettered%20access%20to%20its%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20has%20not%20independently%20confirmed%20Maven's%20use%20in%20Operation%20Epic%20Fury%20nor%20the%20integration%20of%20Anthropic's%20models%20into%20Maven's%20systems.%20Spokespersons%20for%20the%20Pentagon%20and%20Anthropic%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDonald%20Trump%3C%2Fa%3E%20ordered%20all%20federal%20agencies%20to%20stop%20using%20Anthropic's%20products%20within%20six%20months.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanthropic-sues-pentagon-lawsuit-supply-chain-risk-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnthropic%20has%20sued%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Pentagon%2C%20the%20Executive%20Office%20of%20the%20President%2C%20and%20a%20host%20of%20other%20federal%20agencies%20to%20block%20Hegseth%20and%20Trump's%20directives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInitially%20overseen%20by%20Google%2C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-took-over-from-google-on-project-maven-2019-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%20Palantir%20took%20over%20Project%20Maven%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20part%20of%20the%20software%20company's%20highly%20successful%20partnerships%20with%20the%20US%20and%20allied%20governments.%20Karp%20boasted%20last%20year%20that%20Palantir's%20products%20are%20so%20popular%20that%20he%20doesn't%20have%20time%20for%20US%20allies%20who%20hassle%20the%20company%20with%20endless%20meeting%20requests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20telling%20governments%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20look%2C%20we're%20not%20showing%20up%20to%20do%20this%20sales%20call%20for%20Maven%2C%26quot%3B%20Karp%20told%20podcaster%20Molly%20O'Shea%20in%20November%202025.%20%26quot%3BYou%20know%20it%20works.%20We%20know%20it%20works.%20Show%20up%20to%20my%20office%20and%20explain%20how%20you're%20going%20to%20make%20this%20easy%20for%20us%2C%20because%20we%20don't%20have%20huge%20bandwidth.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-project-maven-ai-demonstration-pentagon-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773738421000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b8302aa7a4f9df67ba6617%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-project-maven-ai-demonstration-pentagon-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Cameron%20Staley%2C%20the%20Pentagon's%20chief%20digital%20and%20AI%20officer%2C%20praised%20Palantir's%20tool%20for%20modernizing%20warfighting.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bgriffiths%40insider.com%20(Brent%20D.%20Griffiths)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpalantir-project-maven-ai-demonstration-pentagon-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I've%20tried%20100%20side%20hustles.%20These%205%20are%20the%20most%20lucrative%20that%20don't%20require%20any%20experience.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222351%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20a%20man%20with%20a%20black%20and%20white%20background%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b839754d65ec51752a132f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221763%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETom%20Blake.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tom%20Blake%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETom%20Blake%2C%2029%2C%20turned%20his%20college%20side-hustle%20experiments%20into%20a%20full-time%20content%20business.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20now%20makes%20a%20six-figure%20living%20by%20testing%20and%20reviewing%20side%20hustles%20on%20YouTube%20and%20Substack.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPaid%20market%20research%20is%20one%20of%20Blake's%20top%20side%20hustle%20recommendations%2C%20offering%20low-stress%20income.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Tom%20Blake%2C%20a%2029-year-old%20YouTuber%20and%20blogger%2C%20about%20his%20experiments%20with%20side%20hustles.%20It's%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20experimenting%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fside-hustles-entrepreneurship-cost-to-start-small-business-capitalism-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eside%20hustles%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202014%20while%20I%20was%20in%20college%20for%20a%20simple%20reason%3A%20I%20needed%20to%20pay%20the%20bills.%20Since%20then%2C%20I've%20tried%20over%20100%20of%20them%20%E2%80%94%20everything%20from%20AI%20website%20generation%20to%20crypto%20reward%20programs%20to%20paid%20shopping.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20read%20a%20lot%20about%20side%20hustles%20on%20Reddit%2C%20and%20many%20just%20didn't%20work%20as%20advertised.%20In%202018%2C%20this%20frustration%20led%20me%20to%20start%20a%20blog%20documenting%20my%20side%20hustle%20tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20studied%20psychology%2C%20minored%20in%20marketing%2C%20and%20interned%20at%20a%20digital%20marketing%20agency%2C%20which%20became%20my%20first%20job%20after%20graduating.%20I%20kept%20side%20hustling%20because%20the%20job%20had%20a%20pretty%20low%20starting%20salary%2C%20and%20I%20wanted%20to%20build%20wealth%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20then%20realized%20I%20could%20make%20more%20money%20on%20my%20own%20outside%20my%20job%20if%20I%20worked%20hard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fca01e05-504e-4c32-8bfc-2128cc3e8930%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20content%20business%20is%20now%20my%20full-time%20job%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20the%20blog%20grew%20steadily%2C%20and%20my%20content%20business%20%E2%80%94%20including%20my%20main%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20a%20smaller%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20some%20blogs%2C%20and%20an%20email%20newsletter%20%E2%80%94%20became%20my%20full-time%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20ad%20revenue%20and%20affiliate%20links%2C%20it%20made%20about%20%241%2C700%20in%20its%20first%20year%2C%20then%20about%20%247%2C000%20the%20next%2C%20and%20%2420%2C000%20the%20year%20after.%20Over%20its%20lifetime%2C%20it%20generated%20more%20than%20%241%20million%20in%20revenue%20before%20I%20sold%20it%20at%20the%20end%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20I've%20become%20a%20digital%20nomad%20earning%20six%20figures%20by%20testing%20side%20hustles%20and%20online%20gigs%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40TomBlakeFinance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EYouTube%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwifiwealth.substack.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESubstack%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20make%20about%20%242%2C500%20a%20month%20from%20side%20hustles%2C%20including%20gig%20apps%2C%20money-making%20websites%2C%20investing%2C%20consulting%2C%20and%20freelance%20gigs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20five%20of%20the%20most%20lucrative%20and%20realistic%20side%20hustles%20I've%20found%2C%20especially%20for%20beginners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f324cad1-cf45-4dd0-9133-36d5bae42b12%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Paid%20market%20research%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20one%20of%20the%20simplest%20ways%20I've%20ever%20made%20money%2C%20and%20I%20still%20do%20it%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20need%20feedback%20from%20real%20people.%20Sometimes%20they're%20looking%20for%20niche%20groups%20like%20accountants%20or%20grocery%20store%20workers%2C%20but%20you%20can%20join%20platforms%20to%20find%20open%20focus%20groups%20or%20market%20research%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETypically%2C%20you%20apply%20for%20studies%20through%20platforms%20like%20User%20Interviews%20or%20Respondent.%20If%20you're%20selected%2C%20you%20join%20a%20Zoom%20call%20with%20a%20researcher%2C%20answer%20questions%20for%2030%20to%2060%20minutes%2C%20and%20get%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pay%20varies%20widely%2C%20but%20it's%20common%20to%20earn%20%2450%20to%20%2480%20for%20a%20half-hour%20session%2C%20or%20%2475%20to%20%24100%20for%20an%20hour.%20A%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20I%20did%20a%2045-minute%20conversation%20about%20AI%20and%20earned%20%24200.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20is%20that%20you%20won't%20qualify%20for%20most%20studies%20you%20apply%20to%2C%20and%20you%20have%20to%20apply%20to%20each%20one.%20Still%2C%20I%20can%20usually%20land%20one%20every%20month%20or%20two%2C%20and%20the%20work%20is%20easy%20and%20low-stress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22955bef03-27bc-41fa-92eb-d742c587f10b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Niche%20gig%20economy%20apps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20people%20think%20of%20the%20gig%20economy%20as%20Uber%20or%20DoorDash%2C%20but%20there's%20a%20whole%20world%20of%20lesser-known%20apps%20that%20can%20be%20pretty%20lucrative.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20example%20is%20Sharetown.%20It%20partners%20with%20mattress%20and%20furniture%20brands%20to%20handle%20oversize%20returns%20%E2%80%94%20things%20like%20sofas%20and%20mattresses%20that%20retailers%20don't%20want%20back%20in%20their%20warehouses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20Sharetown%20rep%2C%20you%20pick%20up%20returned%20items%20from%20customers%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-sell-on-facebook-marketplace-beginners-side-hustle-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eresell%20them%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20split%20the%20proceeds%20with%20the%20company.%20Sharetown%20tells%20you%20what%20to%20pick%20up%20and%20what%20price%20to%20list%20it%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20spoken%20with%20reps%20who%20make%20a%20few%20thousand%20dollars%20a%20month%2C%20especially%20in%20busy%20areas.%20You%20need%20a%20vehicle%20that%20can%20haul%20large%20items%2C%20but%20for%20the%20right%20person%2C%20it's%20a%20clever%20way%20to%20start%20a%20flipping%20business%20with%20almost%20no%20upfront%20risk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20apps%20like%20Dolly%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-nyc-low-salary-side-hustle-make-extra-money-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELugg%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20pay%20people%20to%20help%20with%20moving%20jobs.%20You%20can%20sign%20up%20as%20a%20driver%20if%20you%20have%20a%20vehicle%2C%20or%20just%20as%20a%20helper%20if%20you%20don't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222deb999b-e29a-4e0c-8eda-9ce00b7e9972%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Rewards%20and%20discovery%20apps%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ERewards%20apps%20have%20improved%20a%20lot%20in%20recent%20years.%20They're%20apps%20that%20pay%20users%20for%20downloading%20apps%2C%20playing%20mobile%20games%2C%20and%20trying%20products%20and%20services.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20use%20Scrambly.%20I've%20earned%20more%20than%20%241%2C000%20using%20it%20in%20testing%20over%20the%20last%20few%20months.%20One%20offer%20I%20received%20paid%20me%20%24250%20to%20open%20a%20bank%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20recommend%20this%20as%20a%20primary%20source%20of%20income.%20Most%20of%20the%20time%2C%20you're%20earning%20around%20%244-%245%20per%20hour%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20already%20playing%20mobile%20games%20or%20planning%20to%20switch%20bank%20accounts%2C%20it's%20worth%20checking%20them%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2294bb987b-d6b7-4d49-a0c4-1b44eab4020a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20AI%20training%20and%20data%20annotation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20new%20side%20hustle%20I've%20been%20testing%20is%20AI%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20companies%20hire%20human%20testers%20to%20review%20AI-generated%20outputs%20from%20different%20models%20and%20rate%20them%2C%20helping%20improve%20them%20over%20time.%20It's%20essentially%20quality%20assurance%20for%20artificial%20intelligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20started%20testing%20this%20space%20and%20was%20accepted%20into%20a%20platform%20called%20Micro1.%20After%20a%2020-minute%20screening%20process%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20apply%20for%20paid%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPay%20rates%20vary%20dramatically.%20Some%20roles%20pay%20only%20a%20few%20dollars%20an%20hour%2C%20while%20more%20specialized%20projects%2C%20such%20as%20those%20that%20require%20a%20Ph.D.%20in%20a%20specific%20field%2C%20can%20pay%20%2425%20to%20%2450%20or%20more.%20The%20work%20is%20fairly%20steady%2C%20and%20some%20even%20offer%2030%20to%2040%20hours%20a%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22862129ed-c15d-4a54-ac52-fdc4f7f1a3ed%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Website%20and%20app%20testing%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20another%20side%20hustle%20I%20did%20frequently%20in%20college%20and%20still%20recommend%20for%20beginners%20through%20sites%20such%20as%20PlaytestCloud%2C%20Userlytics%2C%20and%20Trymata.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20pay%20users%20to%20test%20websites%20and%20apps%20under%20development.%20You%20follow%20the%20instructions%20or%20navigate%20the%20product%20yourself%2C%20then%20share%20honest%20feedback.%20Most%20tests%20pay%20%2410%20to%20%2420%20and%20take%20about%2015%20to%2020%20minutes.%20Longer%20tests%20of%20up%20to%20an%20hour%20can%20pay%20%2450%20to%20%24100.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20downside%20is%20that%20you%20have%20to%20sign%20up%20and%20claim%20the%20tests%20while%20they're%20available%2C%20on%20a%20first%20come%20first%20serve%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef7ee72c-e363-4c48-b132-f5fd8818b3a8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELessons%20I've%20learned%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESide%20hustles%20can%20be%20exciting%2C%20and%20I%20think%20people%20should%20experiment%20with%20them%2C%20but%20if%20something%20sounds%20too%20good%20to%20be%20true%2C%20it%20probably%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20trying%20anything%2C%20I%20always%20recommend%20reading%20reviews%20and%20checking%20forums%20as%20part%20of%20basic%20due%20diligence.%20If%20someone%20online%20is%20promising%20massive%20hourly%20earnings%20with%20no%20downside%2C%20that's%20a%20red%20flag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-lucrative-side-hustles-tried-no-experience-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773738301000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b83903a96e437d6eb86142%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-lucrative-side-hustles-tried-no-experience-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Tom%20Blake%2C%20now%20a%20digital%20nomad%2C%20has%20tried%20more%20than%20100%20side%20hustles.%20He%20says%20many%20don't%20live%20up%20to%20the%20hype%20but%20a%20few%20are%20worth%20your%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Elle%20Hardy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmost-lucrative-side-hustles-tried-no-experience-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Infighting%20Cost%20Congress%20Dear%20In%20Haryana%20Rajya%20Sabha%20Polls%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Tensions%20between%20senior%20Congress%20leaders%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Hooda%20and%20Kumari%20Selja%20resurfaced%2