20to%20take%20the%20leap%20%E2%80%94%20and%20her%20advice%20for%20young%20professionals.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20summer%2C%20Bushra%20Amiwala%20faced%20a%20career-defining%20choice%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-google-early-retirement-digital-nomad-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estay%20at%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20quit%20to%20run%20for%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20May%2C%20Democratic%20Rep.%20Jan%20Schakowsky%2C%20who%20represents%20Illinois%209th%20District%2C%20announced%20she%20would%20not%20seek%20reelection.%20With%20the%20seat%20open%2C%20Amiwala%20said%20she%20began%20weighing%20a%20run%2C%20speaking%20with%20more%20than%20100%20district%20residents%20in%20and%20around%20Skokie%2C%20where%20she%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20she%20weighed%20the%20decision%2C%20Amiwala%2C%2028%2C%20said%20she%20applied%20for%20a%20six-month%20unpaid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-wish-did-before-quit-job-google-what-did-right-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleave%20of%20absence%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20Google.%20When%20her%20request%20was%20denied%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20left%20with%20two%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDo%20I%20run%20for%20this%20seat%20and%20quit%20my%20job%2C%20or%20do%20I%20stay%20at%20Google%20and%20never%20try%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20In%20June%2C%20Amiwala%20announced%20her%20candidacy%2C%20and%20on%20August%2030%2C%20she%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employee-quit-tech-job-phd-grad-school-career-change-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresigned%20from%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20run%20her%20campaign%20full-time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20year%2C%20I've%20interviewed%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20people%20%E2%80%94%20many%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-meta-google-microsoft-big-tech-workers-quit-job-market-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBig%20Tech%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20who%20quit%20their%20jobs%20without%20having%20another%20role%20lined%20up.%20They've%20become%20outliers%20in%20an%20economy%20where%20people%20are%20quitting%20at%20near-decade%20lows%20%E2%80%94%20a%20trend%20fueled%20by%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-tech-job-market-hiring-cracked-layoffs-amazon-microsoft-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehiring%20slowdown%20across%20tech%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20sectors%20that%20has%20left%20many%20holding%20tightly%20to%20their%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20leaving%20their%20jobs%2C%20some%20took%20relatively%20safe%20paths%2C%20eventually%20joining%20other%20companies%20in%20similar%20roles.%20Others%20made%20riskier%20bets%2C%20launching%20startups%20or%20pursuing%20entirely%20new%20careers.%20Amiwala%20took%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20leap%3A%20leaving%20Google%20to%20run%20for%20Congress%2C%20part%20of%20a%20small%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnewsletters%2Fwomen-rule%2F2025%2F04%2F11%2Fgen-z-politicians-dont-want-to-wait-their-turn-00286160%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20wave%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20younger%20Americans%20entering%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20idea%20of%20solving%20problems%20for%20people%20to%20make%20their%20lives%20easier%20has%20always%20inspired%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Amiwala%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20is%20speaking%20with%20workers%20who've%20found%20themselves%20at%20a%20corporate%20crossroads%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20due%20to%20a%20layoff%2C%20resignation%2C%20job%20search%2C%20or%20shifting%20workplace%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EShare%20your%20story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSechTVqVWQve8iqYssNriCXdtwwdgGRixNNZpmslSKBQqIJ8g%2Fviewform%3Fusp%3Dheader%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilling%20out%20this%20form%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20contacting%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ajzinkula%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ejzinkula%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20or%20via%20Signal%20at%20jzinkula.29.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22bb7bfaeb-1533-4e3a-ba16-d9e4380af3c9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20asked%20herself%202%20questions%20before%20quitting%20Google%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20Amiwala's%20first%20time%20running%20for%20office.%20In%202018%2C%20she%20lost%20a%20bid%20for%20Cook%20County%20commissioner.%20But%20a%20year%20later%2C%20while%20enrolled%20at%20DePaul%20University%2C%20she%20ran%20for%20the%20Skokie%20Board%20of%20Education%20and%20won.%20At%2021%2C%20she%20became%20one%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F03%2F30%2Fmeet-bushra-amiwala-one-of-the-first-gen-z-women-to-hold-public-office-in-the-us.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20first%20members%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Gen%20Z%20elected%20to%20public%20office%20in%20the%20US.%20She%20balanced%20this%20part-time%20role%20with%20a%20sales%20associate%20job%20at%20Google%20based%20in%20Chicago%2C%20which%20she%20started%20after%20graduating%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20financial%20implications%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-leave-google-job-no-regrets-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleaving%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuge%20consideration%26quot%3B%20for%20Amiwala.%20She%20said%20one%20reason%20she%20didn't%20pursue%20public%20service%20full-time%20sooner%20was%20that%20she%20wanted%20to%20provide%20financial%20support%20for%20her%20immigrant%20parents%20%E2%80%94%20and%20saw%20tech%20as%20a%20more%20stable%20path.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20these%20concerns%2C%20Amiwala%20said%20two%20questions%20helped%20her%20get%20comfortable%20with%20leaving%20Google.%20The%20first%20was%2C%20%26quot%3BAre%20you%20all%20talk%20and%20no%20action%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20always%20talking%20about%20how%20I'd%20love%20to%20be%20able%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20in%20Congress%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20it's%20like%2C%20are%20you%20all%20talk%3F%20Are%20you%20actually%20going%20to%20do%20it%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20question%20was%20whether%2C%20five%20or%2010%20years%20from%20now%2C%20she%20would%20regret%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20was%20a%20no-brainer%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20knew%20I'd%20regret%20not%20doing%20it%2C%20and%20that%20matrix%20of%20decision-making%20made%20it%20really%20easy%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20resigning%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20taken%20some%20comfort%20from%20the%20savings%20and%20equity%20she'd%20accumulated%20over%20the%20years.%20She%20decided%20not%20to%20pay%20herself%20a%20salary%20from%20her%20campaign%20funds%20but%20has%20occasionally%20received%20small%20speaking%20stipends%2C%20which%20have%20helped%20cover%20some%20expenses.%20To%20cut%20costs%2C%20she%20said%20she's%20%26quot%3Bdeflated%26quot%3B%20her%20lifestyle%2C%20cutting%20back%20on%20dinners%20with%20friends%20and%20personal%20training%20appointments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20lifestyle%20inflation%20that%20happens%20when%20working%20at%20a%20tech%20role%20that%20just%20isn't%20as%20necessary%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d48f8315-70c8-4fa2-a6b4-e8bf0dc2ad5b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdvice%20for%20young%20professionals%20%E2%80%94%20and%20aspiring%20politicians%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFifteen%20Democrats%2C%20including%20Amiwala%2C%20and%20four%20Republicans%20are%20running%20for%20the%20congressional%20seat%20in%20the%20March%2017%20primary.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdailynorthwestern.com%2F2026%2F03%2F12%2Fcity%2Fabughamentum-making-ground-against-biss-9th-district-poll-indicates%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERecent%20polling%3C%2Fa%3E%20points%20to%20three%20leading%20Democratic%20candidates%3A%20Evanston%20Mayor%20Daniel%20Biss%2C%20Internet%20content%20creator%20Kat%20Abughazaleh%2C%20and%20Illinois%20state%20Sen.%20Laura%20Fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmiwala%20said%20she's%20focused%20on%20her%20campaign%20and%20hasn't%20yet%20thought%20seriously%20about%20what%20would%20come%20next%20if%20she%20loses%20the%20election.%20But%20she's%20navigated%20challenges%20before%20in%20her%20career.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20summer%20after%20her%20junior%20year%20at%20DePaul%2C%20where%20she%20studied%20management%20information%20systems%2C%20she%20interned%20at%20a%20large%20consulting%20firm%20%E2%80%94%20but%20did%20not%20receive%20a%20return%20offer.%20That%20fall%2C%20during%20her%20senior%20year%2C%20she%20applied%20for%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-jobs-careers-hiring%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erole%20at%20Google%3C%2Fa%3E%20without%20a%20referral%20and%2C%20after%20a%20few%20interviews%2C%20received%20an%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmiwala's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcareer-advice-for-young-adults-to-succeed-tough-job-market-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eadvice%20for%20young%20professionals%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20It's%20unrealistic%20to%20expect%20your%20career%20to%20fulfill%20the%20financial%2C%20emotional%2C%20and%20spiritual%20aspects%20of%20your%20life%20that%20matter%20most.%20So%20you%20might%20have%20to%20look%20outside%20your%20job%20for%20these%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20considering%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fworkers-job-hugging-hopping-labor-market-growth-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleaving%20their%20jobs%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20run%20for%20office%2C%20she%20recommends%20speaking%20with%20community%20leaders%20who%20can%20provide%20insight%20into%20the%20issues%20constituents%20care%20about.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EShe%20said%20that%20running%20for%20office%20isn't%20the%20only%20way%20to%20get%20involved%20politically%2C%20but%20that%20if%20you're%20considering%20it%2C%20it%20could%20be%20a%20sign%20you're%20well-suited%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20very%20specific%20type%20of%20person%20who%20thinks%20about%20running%20for%20office%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20average%20person%20does%20not%20think%20like%20that.%20So%20if%20that%20is%20something%20that%20interests%20you%20and%20you%20feel%20uniquely%20equipped%20to%20do%20it%20successfully%2C%20you%20absolutely%20should.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zer-quit-google-job-run-for-congress-big-tech-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773737881000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b82bcda96e437d6eb85f75%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zer-quit-google-job-run-for-congress-big-tech-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Gen%20Zer%20quit%20her%20Google%20job%20to%20run%20for%20Congress%20in%20Illinois.%20She%20shares%20why%20she%20left%20Big%20Tech%2C%20and%20her%20advice%20for%20young%20professionals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jzinkula%40insider.com%20(Jacob%20Zinkula)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-zer-quit-google-job-run-for-congress-big-tech-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rebecca%20Ferguson%20gets%20one%20scene%20in%20Dune%203%3B%20'There%E2%80%99s%20a%20lot%20of%20FOMO'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773737878000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129628340%2Cimgsize-133946.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainme