9df67ba61df%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221334%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETSA%20agents%20have%20been%20working%20without%20pay%20for%20the%20last%20month%20as%20the%20result%20of%20a%20partial%20government%20shutdown.%3Cp%3EAnnabelle%20GORDON%20%2F%20AFP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETSA%20agents%20have%20gone%20unpaid%20for%20the%20last%20month%2C%20causing%20delays%20at%20some%20airports.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20because%20of%20the%20ongoing%20DHS%20shutdown%2C%20spurred%20by%20disagreements%20over%20ICE%20funding.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20where%20things%20stand%20with%20the%20ongoing%20partial%20government%20shutdown.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you've%20been%20to%20the%20airport%20in%20the%20US%20lately%2C%20you%20may%20have%20encountered%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftsa-delays-which-airports-have-long-lines-how-to-check-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elong%20lines%20at%20security%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20Transportation%20Security%20Administration%20(TSA)%20agents%20have%20been%20working%20without%20pay%20since%20mid-February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20those%20agents%2C%20fed%20up%20with%20the%20situation%2C%20have%20begun%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fairport-security-wait-times-tsa-agent-shortage-government-shutdown-dhs-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecalling%20in%20sick%20or%20even%20quitting%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20according%20to%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20why%20aren't%20agents%20getting%20paid%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2237cb32c8-78ca-457f-9509-b8646e085310%5C%22%3EA%20long%20but%20largely%20ignored%20partial%20government%20shutdown%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20may%20not%20have%20realized%20it%2C%20but%20the%20US%20has%20been%20in%20a%20partial%20government%20shutdown%20since%20February%2014.%20It's%20already%20the%20third-longest%20shutdown%20in%20American%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Bshutdown%26quot%3B%20occurs%20when%20lawmakers%20in%20Washington%20fail%20to%20pass%20a%20bill%20to%20fund%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20government.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-vote-government-reopened-longest-shutdown-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elongest-ever%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20occurred%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20lasted%2043%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20this%20one's%20different%20because%20every%20department%20has%20been%20funded%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20fiscal%20year%2C%20except%20one%3A%20the%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20department%20oversees%20several%20agencies%2C%20including%20not%20just%20TSA%2C%20but%20also%20the%20Federal%20Emergency%20Management%20Agency%20(FEMA)%2C%20the%20Coast%20Guard%2C%20and%20%E2%80%94%20most%20significantly%20%E2%80%94%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)%20and%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Protection%20(CBP).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226585f94f-4210-4ea3-8b3b-37eed173f41e%5C%22%3EIt%20all%20goes%20back%20to%20Minneapolis%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJust%20a%20couple%20of%20months%20ago%2C%20none%20of%20this%20seemed%20like%20it%20would%20happen.%20Then%2C%20Alex%20Pretti%20was%20shot%20by%20border%20patrol%20officers%20in%20Minneapolis%20on%20January%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPretti's%20death%2C%20along%20with%20the%20fatal%20shooting%20of%20Ren%C3%A9e%20Good%20two%20weeks%20earlier%2C%20led%20to%20outrage%20among%20Democrats%20on%20Capitol%20Hill%2C%20who%20demanded%20reforms%20to%20both%20CBP%20and%20ICE%20before%20they%20would%20agree%20to%20fund%20the%20agencies%20any%20further.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Republicans%20have%20a%20majority%20in%20both%20chambers%2C%20the%20Senate's%2060-vote%20%26quot%3Bfilibuster%26quot%3B%20rule%20means%20that%20Democratic%20votes%20are%20needed%20to%20pass%20major%20funding%20legislation%2C%20given%20that%20there%20are%20just%2053%20GOP%20senators.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Pretti%20shooting%20happened%20just%20before%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgovernment-shutdown-odds-polymarket-kalshi-minnesota-ice-shooting-alex-pretti-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epackage%20of%20government%20funding%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20the%20bill%20to%20fund%20DHS%2C%20was%20set%20to%20come%20up%20for%20a%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20in%20both%20parties%20ultimately%20agreed%20to%20strip%20DHS%20funding%20from%20the%20package%20and%20pass%20the%20rest%2C%20and%20there%20was%20only%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-government-partial-shutdown-minnesota-homeland-security-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebrief%20shutdown%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20end%20of%20January%2C%20largely%20due%20to%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-signs-bill-ending-shutdown-teeing-up-dhs-funding-battle-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ekicked%20off%20negotiations%3C%2Fa%3E%20between%20Democrats%20and%20Republicans%20over%20DHS%20funding%2C%20which%20have%20largely%20stalled%20in%20recent%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223834448c-0e85-4919-8242-8845ba2b58a0%5C%22%3EWhere%20things%20stand%20right%20now%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221604%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22TSA%20lines%20at%20William%20P.%20Hobby%20Airport%20in%20Houston.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69aeed08d3e2f1aef36a3a99%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221198%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETSA%20lines%20at%20William%20P.%20Hobby%20Airport%20in%20Houston.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Houston%20Airports%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDemocrats%20have%20laid%20out%20a%20series%20of%20demands%20for%20ICE%20and%20CBP%2C%20including%20ending%20roving%20patrols%20and%20tightening%20arrest%20warrant%20rules%2C%20increasing%20accountability%20measures%20for%20ICE%2C%20including%20independent%20investigations%2C%20and%20adding%20body%20cameras%20and%20removing%20masks%20from%20ICE%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20publicly%20rejected%20many%20of%20those%20points%2C%20and%20while%20the%20two%20sides%20have%20exchanged%20proposals%2C%20negotiations%20have%20largely%20stalled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20Democrats%20in%20both%20the%20House%20and%20the%20Senate%20have%20begun%20to%20press%20for%20bills%20that%20would%20fund%20DHS%20except%20for%20ICE%20and%20CBP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20letter%20to%20colleagues%20sent%20on%20Monday%2C%20House%20Minority%20Leader%20Hakeem%20Jeffries%20announced%20that%20Democrats%20would%20try%20to%20force%20a%20vote%20on%20a%20bill%20to%20do%20just%20that%20in%20the%20coming%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Senate%20Democrats%20have%20tried%20to%20pass%20similar%20legislation%2C%20but%20have%20also%20been%20blocked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepublicans%20have%20largely%20objected%20to%20these%20efforts%20out%20of%20concern%20that%2C%20should%20those%20bills%20pass%2C%20Democrats%20will%20have%20little%20incentive%20to%20continue%20negotiating%20on%20ICE%20and%20CBP%2C%20potentially%20leaving%20those%20agencies%20without%20funding%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-tsa-agents-not-paid-right-homeland-security-shutdown-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773737221000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b80c90a96e437d6eb85bf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-tsa-agents-not-paid-right-homeland-security-shutdown-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Department%20of%20Homeland%20Security%20has%20been%20shut%20down%20since%20February%2014%2C%20with%20lawmakers%20still%20at%20odds%20over%20funding%20for%20ICE%20and%20Border%20Patrol.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22bmetzger%40insider.com%20(Bryan%20Metzger)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-tsa-agents-not-paid-right-homeland-security-shutdown-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China's%20biggest%20names%20in%20tech%20are%20piling%20into%20the%20OpenClaw%20gold%20rush%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22OpenClaw%20in%20China%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b8f8874d65ec51752a1cde%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223998%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETencent%2C%20Alibaba%2C%20and%20others%20are%20piling%20into%20OpenClaw%20as%20China%20races%20to%20adopt%20the%20AI%20agent.%3Cp%3EADEK%20BERRY%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina's%20biggest%20tech%20names%20all%20want%20a%20piece%20of%20OpenClaw.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETencent%2C%20Alibaba%2C%20ByteDance%2C%20and%20others%20have%20launched%20versions%20of%20the%20AI%20agent%20and%20integrations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOpenClaw%20took%20China%20by%20storm%20in%20recent%20weeks%20as%20the%20phrase%20%26quot%3Braising%20the%20lobster%26quot%3B%20trended%20online.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%26quot%3Blobster%26quot%3B%20craze%20in%20China%20has%20quickly%20turned%20into%20a%20corporate%20land%20grab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20weeks%20of%20OpenClaw%20gaining%20traction%20among%20developers%20and%20hobbyists%2C%20China's%20internet%20giants%20began%20rolling%20out%20their%20own%20versions%20of%20the%20AI%20agent%20and%20integrations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETencent%20launched%20QClaw%20last%20week%2C%20a%20tool%20that%20integrates%20OpenClaw%20into%20WeChat's%20vast%20ecosystem%2C%20China's%20super%20app.%20Users%20can%20send%20a%20message%20directly%20to%20QClaw%20via%20WeChat%2C%20and%20the%20agent%20will%20immediately%20execute%20the%20task%2C%20Tencent%20said%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETikTok%20owner%20ByteDance's%20cloud%20unit%2C%20Volcano%20Engine%2C%20rolled%20out%20ArkClaw%2C%20a%20cloud-based%20version%20of%20OpenClaw%20accessible%20through%20a%20web%20browser.%20Alibaba%20also%20introduced%20JVS%20Claw%2C%20a%20mobile%20app%20designed%20to%20help%20users%20install%20and%20deploy%20OpenClaw%20more%20easily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EXiaomi%2C%20a%20consumer%20electronics%20company%2C%20has%20launched%20a%20closed%20beta%20test%20of%20MiClaw%2C%20an%20AI%20agent%20that%20lets%20users%20control%20Xiaomi%20smartphones%20and%20smart%20home%20devices%20with%20single-sentence%20commands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20startups%20moved%20just%20as%20fast.%20Zhipu%20AI%2C%20Moonshot%20AI%2C%20and%20MiniMax%20have%20released%20large%20language%20models%20or%20frameworks%20built%20on%20top%20of%20OpenClaw.%20Shares%20of%20Zhipu%20AI%20and%20MiniMax%20surged%2013%20per%20cent%20and%2022%20per%20cent%20respectively%20last%20Tuesday%2C%20following%20the%20announcements%20of%20their%20OpenClaw%20tools.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20just%20Chinese%20companies.%20Nvidia%20on%20Monday%20announced%20that%20it%20has%20created%20NemoClaw%2C%20an%20enterprise%20platform%20built%20on%20top%20of%20OpenClaw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20a%20network%20guardrail%2C%20it%20has%20a%20privacy%20router%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20we%20could%20protect%20and%20keep%20the%20claws%20from%20executing%20inside%20our%20company%2C%20and%20do%20it%20safely%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ceo-jensen-huang-openclaw-ai-strategy-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ECEO%20Jensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20during%20Nvidia's%202026%20GTC%20conference%20in%20San%20Jose%20on%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20company%20in%20the%20world%20today%20needs%20to%20have%20an%20OpenClaw%20strategy%2C%20an%20agentic%20system%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20new%20computer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-openclaw-craze-lobster-stock-trading-blind-dates-cyber-pets-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOpenClaw%20has%20taken%20China%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20storm.%20The%20trending%20phrase%20%26quot%3Braising%20the%20lobster%26quot%3B%20went%20viral%2C%20as%20Chinese%20social%20media%20users%20used%20it%20to%20describe%20deploying%20the%20AI%20agent%20to%20automate%20everyday%20tasks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20across%20China%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-openclaw-lobster-craze-uninstall-ai-agent-paid-side-hustle-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erushed%20to%20install%20OpenClaw%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20their%20devices%2C%20forming%20queues%20outside%20Tencent's%20Shenzhen%20headquarters%20and%20Baidu's%20Beijing%20office%20to%20seek%20help%20from%20engineers.%20Others%20turned%20to%20online%20marketplaces%2C%20paying%20strangers%20to%20install%20the%20tool%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20frenzy%20has%20since%20been%20tempered%20by%20growing%20security%20concerns.%20In%20the%20past%20week%2C%20some%20users%20have%20begun%20removing%20the%20software%20%E2%80%94%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20even%20paying%20others%20to%20uninstall%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20in%20February%2C%20China's%20National%20Vulnerability%20Database%2C%20run%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Industry%20and%20Information%20Technology%2C%20warned%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-hires-openclaw-creator-peter-steinberger-personal-ai-agents-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopen-source%20agent%20%3C%2Fa%3Ecould%20introduce%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-openclaw-ai-agent-openai-full-rein-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esecurity%20risks%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20not%20properly%20configured.%20Misconfigured%20deployments%20could%20leave%20systems%20exposed%20to%20cyberattacks%20or%20data%20breaches%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20week%2C