ut-inflation-risks-rise-as-iran-war-drags-on-126031700561_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Findia-growth-forecasts-cut-inflation-risks-rise-as-iran-war-drags-on-126031700561_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22We're%20entering%20the%20golden%20age%20of%20baby%20boomer%20estate%20sales%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225547%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22person%20picking%20up%20china%20at%20a%20sale%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b86976a96e437d6eb8674b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EElena%20Noviello%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20love%20to%20complain%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-boomers-generation-working-not-retiring-selling-homes-miellnnials-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebaby%20boomers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20that%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20stuff.%20They're%20hoarding%20all%20the%20houses%2C%20they're%20keeping%20all%20the%20money%2C%20they're%20materialists%20who%20have%20accumulated%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennial-gen-x-boomer-inheritance-stuff-house-collectibles-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexorbitant%20amount%20of%20possessions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20There%20are%20a%20couple%20of%20problems%20with%20these%20gripes%3A%20For%20one%2C%20no%20generation%20is%20a%20monolith%2C%20and%20everybody%20amasses%20things%20over%20the%20course%20of%20their%20lives%2C%20so%20back%20off.%20But%20more%20importantly%2C%20youths%20and%20slightly-beyond-youths%2C%20the%20stuff%20pileup%20is%20actually%20to%20your%20benefit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20golden%20age%20of%20boomer%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-tips-finding-valuable-treasure-yard-estate-sales-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eestate%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20upon%20us%2C%20and%20while%20you%20probably%20don't%20want%20all%20the%20wedding%20china%20that's%20about%20to%20flood%20the%20market%2C%20there's%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20neat%20stuff%20you%20can%20pick%20up.%20Think%20knickknacks%20for%20Gen%20Z%20maximalists%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmake-home-look-mid-century-for-cheap-according-to-designers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emidcentury%20modern%3C%2Fa%3E%20decor%2C%20and%20so%20much%20silver%20that%20one%20estate%20seller%20says%20the%20weighing%20it%20all%20makes%20her%20team%20%26quot%3Bfeel%20like%20drug%20dealers.%26quot%3B%20Over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20decades%2C%20baby%20boomers'%20stuff%20has%20to%20go%20somewhere%2C%20and%20that%20rehoming%20process%20is%20increasingly%20taking%20place%20at%20estate%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20call%20it%20the%20tsunami%20of%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Julie%20Hall%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20American%20Society%20of%20Estate%20Liquidators.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20cresting.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20%E2%80%A6%20a%20lot%20of%20baby%20boomers.%20America's%20over-65%20population%20reached%2055.8%20million%20in%202020%2C%20and%20an%20additional%2042.4%20million%20are%20in%20the%2055-64%20age%20group%20(which%2C%20yes%2C%20catches%20some%20Gen%20Xers).%20This%20adds%20up%20to%20nearly%20100%20million%20people%20who%20have%20amassed%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20possessions%20%E2%80%94%20stuff%20they%20bought%2C%20stuff%20they%20got%20from%20their%20own%20parents%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-junk-clutter-baby-boomer-parents-family-storage-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estuff%20their%20kids%3C%2Fa%3E%20stuck%20them%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20kept%20everything%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Sarah%20Hersh%2C%20one%20of%20the%20owners%20of%20Ben%20Hersh%20Estate%20Sales%20in%20New%20Jersey.%20Boomers%20were%20the%20first%20American%20generation%20to%20come%20up%20in%20an%20era%20of%20mass%20production%20and%20blatant%20consumerism%2C%20and%20many%20of%20the%20things%20they%20bought%20were%20built%20to%20last.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20we%20go%20into%20these%20houses%20of%20the%20boomer%20generation%2C%20they're%20packed%20to%20the%20rafters%20with%20stuff%20from%20the%20mid-century%20to%20current.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20elders%20would%20prefer%20to%20keep%20all%20of%20this%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-stuff-avalanche-millennial-children-inheritance-tough-conversations-homes-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estuff%20in%20the%20family%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20their%20kids%2C%20grandkids%2C%20nieces%2C%20and%20nephews%20don't%20want%20to%20inherit%20much%2C%20or%20simply%20don't%20have%20the%20space.%20Enter%20the%20estate%20sale%20%E2%80%94%20pop-up%20limited-time%20museums%20of%20a%20person's%20life%2C%20where%20everything%20on%20the%20premises%20is%20for%20sale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoomers%20were%20an%20era%20of%20collectors.%20They%20believed%20in%20entertaining%2C%20and%20they%20believed%20their%20possessions%20had%20value%2C%20so%20they%20were%20proud%20to%20amass%20large%20collections%20of%20things%20to%20display%20to%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Hersh%20says.%20%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20really%20live%20like%20that%20anymore%2C%20but%20those%20things%20make%20for%20excellent%20inventory%20for%20resellers%20and%20the%20new%20younger%20generation%20of%20consumers%20who%20are%20into%20that%20vibe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGen%20Z%20likes%20the%20appeal%20of%20sustainability%2C%20plus%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fcottagecore-aesthetic%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethey're%20into%20%26quot%3Bcottagecore%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%26quot%3Bgrandmacore%26quot%3B%20aesthetics.%20Millennials%20and%20Gen%20X%20want%20midcentury%20modern%20and%20utilitarian%20pieces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recognize%20estate%20sales%20can%20sound%20a%20bit%20morbid%20at%20first%2C%20but%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fboomers-retirees-sell-stuff-downsize-retirement-housing-senior-move-manager-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enot%20all%20offloadings%3C%2Fa%3E%20come%20after%20a%20funeral.%20There%20are%20actually%20four%20Ds%20to%20estate%20sales%3A%20downsizing%2C%20divorce%2C%20decorating%2C%20and%2C%20yes%2C%20death.%20That%20latter%20one%20may%20give%20you%20the%20heebie%20jeebies%2C%20but%20as%20the%20saying%20goes%2C%20you%20can't%20take%20it%20with%20you%2C%20and%20there%20are%20plenty%20of%20people%20willing%20to%20scoop%20up%20the%20stuff%20you've%20left%20behind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJanelle%20Stone%2C%20a%20high-end%20estate%20liquidator%2C%20operates%20out%20of%20what%20she%20calls%20the%20%26quot%3Bmecca%20of%20estate%20sales%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20Dallas%20%E2%80%94%20and%20sees%20her%20line%20of%20work%20as%20a%20goldmine.%20After%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmillennials-minimalist-myth-decluttering-buying-things-spending-boomers-gen-z-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edecades%20of%20minimalism%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20fashion%20and%20design%2C%20maximalism%20is%20back.%20She's%20started%20buying%20plate%20hangers%20to%20put%20dishes%20on%20display%20again%20and%20marvels%20at%2020-something%20shoppers%20grabbing%20various%20tchotchkes.%20Furs%20have%20gone%20%26quot%3Binsane%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says%2C%20and%20the%20same%20goes%20for%20vintage%20fashion.%20Customers%20will%20wait%20in%20line%20for%20two%20hours%20for%20a%20Herend%20porcelain%20starfish%20they've%20scoped%20out%20online%20prior%20to%20the%20sale.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20never%20going%20to%20completely%20clear%20a%20house%2C%20but%20it's%20pretty%20amazing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20know%20what%20they%20want%2C%20and%20they%20come%20and%20buy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20huge%20moment%20for%20sterling%2C%20given%20the%20increase%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgold-price-silver-price-today-market-crash-outlook-forecast-warsh-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprice%20of%20silver%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20hit%20an%20all-time%20high%20of%20over%20%24120%20per%20ounce%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20year.%20(It's%20since%20come%20back%20down%20but%20is%20still%20in%20the%20%2485%20range.)%20Stone%20tells%20me%20it's%20affected%20how%20they%20price%20it%20%E2%80%94%20they%20can't%20be%20as%20aggressive%2C%20because%20nobody%20can%20afford%20to%20pay%20%2416%2C000%20for%20an%20eight-piece%20silverware%20set%2C%20and%20the%20smelters%20are%20so%20inundated%20they%20might%20not%20even%20take%20it.%20Hence%20the%20drug%20dealer%20analogy%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20weigh%20it%20out.%20I%20mean%2C%20we%20look%20like%20drug%20dealers%20with%20our%20gram%20scales%20and%20baggies%20everywhere%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHersh%2C%20in%20New%20Jersey%2C%20concurs%20on%20the%20popularity%20of%20sterling%20silver%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famericans-shopping-secondhand-tariffs-recession-goodwill-ebay-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evintage%20clothes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20adds%20that%20vintage%20collectibles%2C%20jewelry%2C%20toys%2C%20and%20electronics%20are%20also%20a%20big%20draw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everything%20is%20flying%20off%20the%20estate%20sale%20shelves.%20Hersh%20says%20midcentury%20modern%20furniture%20still%20sells%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bit's%20not%20as%20strong%20as%20it%20was.%26quot%3B%20Few%20buyers%20are%20into%20china%2C%20etched%20crystal%2C%20and%20glass.%20The%20big%20brown%20furniture%20that's%20long%20sat%20in%20baby%20boomers'%20and%20the%20silent%20generation's%20homes%20often%20goes%20unwanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20general%20rule%20of%20thumb%20is%20the%20bigger%20and%20heavier%20and%20darker%20a%20piece%20is%2C%20the%20more%20likely%20it's%20going%20to%20remain%20there%20and%20not%20be%20sold%2C%26quot%3B%20Hall%20says.%20Younger%20generations%20tend%20to%20prefer%20smaller%2C%20portable%20pieces.%20Hersh%20tells%20me%20clear%20glass%20isn't%20a%20popular%20seller%20%26quot%3Bno%20matter%20what%20you%20do.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20recently%20witnessed%20this%20for%20myself%20at%20an%20estate%20sale%20in%20Long%20Island%2C%20New%20York.%20It%20was%20a%20lazy%20Sunday%2C%20so%20I%20showed%20up%20during%20the%20last%20hour%20of%20a%20five-hour%20sale.%20The%20first%20thing%20I%20noticed%20when%20I%20walked%20into%20the%20kitchen%20was%20two%20sets%20of%20china%2C%20one%20of%20which%20looked%20very%20similar%20to%20the%20set%20my%20mother%20has.%20Around%20the%20corner%20was%20a%20big%20brown%20hutch%20filled%20with%20stacks%20of%20crystal%20and%20clear%20glassware%2C%20and%20there%20was%20more%20in%20the%20basement.%20My%20main%20thought%20was%20we%20should%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fikea-things-not-to-buy-interior-designer-what-to-get-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshut%20down%20Ikea%3C%2Fa%3E%20immediately%20and%20never%20buy%20new%20dishes%20or%20glasses%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-online-business-platforms-based-types-entrepreneurs%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einternet%20has%20changed%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20accelerated%20the%20scale%20of%20the%20estate%20industry%2C%20just%20as%20it%20has%20every%20other%20part%20of%20the%20economy.%20Everyone%20can%20look%20up%20what%20everything%20costs%2C%20so%20sellers%20have%20to%20do%20their%20research%20and%20can't%20simply%20guesstimate%20a%20fair%20price%20anymore.%20Sellers%20often%20post%20what's%20available%20online%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20so%20buyers%20can%20pinpoint%20exactly%20what%20they%20want%20before%20they%20show%20up%20in%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhustle-culture-what-its-really-like-reselling-clothing-for-profit-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20resellers%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20technology%20has%20given%20birth%20to%20a%20plethora%20of%20resale%20platforms%2C%20from%20eBay%20to%20Depop%20to%20Whatnot%2C%20and%20droves%20of%20people%20eager%20to%20turn%20flipping%20used%20stuff%20into%20a%20side%20hustle%20or%20even%20a%20full-time%20gig.%20Most%20of%20the%20estate%20sellers%20and%20aficionados%20I%20spoke%20to%20for%20this%20story%20had%20tales%20about%20this%20development.%20Hersh%20tells%20me%20resellers%20are%20%26quot%3Bvicious%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20on%20certain%20sales%2C%20flipped%20me%20up%20the%20first%2050%20people%20in%20line.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20like%20elbowing%20each%20other%20out%20of%20spaces%20to%20get%20to%20stuff%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHall%20points%20out%20that%20the%20resellers%20are%20generally%20a%20positive%20for%20estate%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%2C%20the%20goal%20is%20to%20get%20rid%20of%20everything%20in%20the%20house%2C%20and%20who%20cares%20if%20someone%20plans%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Febay-ceo-jamie-iannone-gold-mine-average-household-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eput%20it%20on%20eBay%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20triple%20the%20price.%20But%20they%20can%20be%20pushy%2C%20asking%20for%20deals.%20%26quot%3BResellers%20sometimes%20want%20more%20of%20a%20bargain%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20times%20we%20cannot%20give%20it%20to%20them%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20for%20the%20faint%20of%20heart.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20cool%20bar%20at%20an%20estate%20sale%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b81f7f4d65ec51752a0fbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222268%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20recent%20estate%20sale%20experience%20included%20this%20very%20cool%20basement%20bar%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20unwanted%20items.%3Cp%3EEmily%20Stewart%2FBusiness%20insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMaddy%20Brannon%2C%20an%20estate%20sale%20influencer%20based%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20says%20she%20prefers%20to%20hit%20up%20estate%20sales%20later%20in%20the%20day%20so%20she%20doesn't%20have%20to%20duke%20it%20out%20with%20the%20pros.%20She%20stumbled%20into%20the%20market%20when%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20were%20looking%20to%20furnish%20their%20home%2C%20and%20now%20she%20uses%20her%20experience%20to%20pass%20along%20useful%20tips%20to%20the%20noobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%20to%20be%20the%20first%20person%20at%20the%20estate%20sale%20unless%20you%20saw%20something%20on%20the%20listing%20you%20absolutely%20have%20to%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%20She's%20not%20sure%20if%20it's%20the%20%26quot%3BDisney%20World%20effect%26quot%3B%20or%20what%2C%20but%20people%20worry%20about%20long%20lines%20and%20feel%20like%20they%20must%20be%20first%20in%20at%20all%20costs.%20Plus%2C%20later%20in%20the%20day%2C%20you're%20more%20likely%20to%20get%20a%20discount.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBrannon's%20other%20pieces%20of%20advice%20included%20going%20during%20the%20week%20to%20avoid%20crowds%20and%20making%20sure%20you%20understand%20the%20rules%20of%20getting%20in%20%E2%80%94%20for%20some%20sales%2C%20waiting%20in%20line%20isn't%20enough.%20Instead%2C%20the%20executor%20will%20call%20you%20in%20by%20name%20or%20number.%20And%20don't%20shop%20off%20the%20%26quot%3Bhold%26quot%3B%20table%2C%20where%20shoppers%20place%20items%20they%20want%20to%20buy.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20get%20really%20upset%20about%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20genuinely%20something%20quite%20nice%20to%20all%20of%20this%2C%20albeit%20awkward.%20We%20spend%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdownsizing-move-more-family-time-less-money-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eour%20lives%20accumulating%20things%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%2C%20over%20time%2C%20getting%20attached%20to%20them.%20Getting%20rid%20of%20them%20can%20be%20emotionally%20fraught%2C%20especially%20if%20we'd%20hoped%20our%20loved%20ones%20would%20want%20them%20or%20believed%20they'd%20hold%20more%20value%20than%20they%20do.%20For%20many%20people%2C%20it's%20a%20hard%20pill%20to%20swallow%20that%20their%20kids%20don't%20want%20their%20prized%20tea%20set%2C%20but%20acknowledging%20that%20is%20also%20permission%20to%20let%20it%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20a%20peculiar%20sense%20of%20intimacy%20to%20estate%20sales%20%E2%80%94%20you%20walk%20through%20someone's%20home%2C%20touch%20their%20things%2C%20look%20through%20their%20drawers%2C%20and%20get%20to%20make%20up%20stories%20about%20them%20based%20on%20their%20possessions.%20The%20golden%20age%20of%20estate%20sales%20isn't%20just%20about%20the%20%26quot%3Bgoldmine%26quot%3B%20of%20inventory%20or%20the%20%26quot%3Bvicious%26quot%3B%20hustle%20of%20the%20resale%20market%2C%20it's%20about%20the%20way%20we%20experience%20life%20through%20tangible%20items%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20those%20things%20can%20live%20multiple%20lives%2C%20even%20ones%20we're%20not%20involved%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20next%20time%20you%20see%20an%20estate%20sale%20nearby%20because%20your%20boomer%20neighbors%20are%20finally%20selling%20their%20family%20home%20and%20moving%20to%20a%20condo%20in%20Florida%2C%20instead%20of%20begrudging%20that%20it%20took%20so%20long%2C%20pop%20over%20to%20see%20if%20you%20can%20pick%20up%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Floud-luxury-items-popular-designer-brands-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evintage%20Le%20Creuset%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Femily-stewart%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EEmily%20Stewart%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20is%20a%20senior%20correspondent%20at%20Business%20Insider%2C%20writing%20about%