tive.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20co-CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-sarandos-wbd-price-politics-trump-interview-paramount-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETed%20Sarandos%3C%2Fa%3E%20doesn't%20think%20AI%20slop%20will%20rule%20the%20entertainment%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20think%20faster%20and%20cheaper%20matters%20if%20it's%20not%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said%20of%20using%20AI%20in%20a%20new%20interview%20with%20POLITICO%2C%20which%2C%20like%20Business%20Insider%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20most%20competitive%20time%20in%20the%20history%20of%20media.%20So%20you've%20got%20to%20be%20better%20every%20time%20out%20of%20the%20gate.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstartups-investors-ai-hollywood-pitch-decks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20startups%3C%2Fa%3E%20building%20tools%20for%20entertainment%20companies%20and%20creatives%20%E2%80%94%20from%20special%20effects%20to%20content%20generation%20%E2%80%94%20have%20been%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-hollywood-pitch-decks-raised-millions-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrowing%20presence%20in%20Hollywood%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Netflix%20recently%20acquired%20InterPositive%2C%20an%20AI%20startup%20that%20develops%20tools%20for%20filmmakers%2C%20founded%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fben-affleck-net-worth%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eactor%20Ben%20Affleck%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20focus%20is%20that%20AI%20should%20be%20a%20creator%20tool%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20told%20POLITICO.%20%26quot%3BThe%20same%20way%20production%20tools%20have%20evolved%20over%20time%2C%20AI%20is%20just%20a%20rapid%2C%20important%20evolution%20of%20these%20tools.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESa