-strike-afghanistan-civilian-deaths-126031700431_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Findia-condemns-pakistan-kabul-hospital-strike-afghanistan-civilian-deaths-126031700431_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fexternal-affairs-defence-security%2Fnews%2Findia-condemns-pakistan-kabul-hospital-strike-afghanistan-civilian-deaths-126031700431_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22YouTube%20star%20Mark%20Rober%20got%20a%20big%20boost%20in%20product%20sales%20after%20his%20Netflix%20deal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22CHRISTMAS%20IN%20ROCKEFELLER%20CENTER%20--%20NBC%2FHershey%20Tree%20Lighting%20Viewing%20Party%20--%20Pictured%3A%20Mark%20Rober%20--%20(Photo%20by%3A%20Noam%20Galai%2FNBC%20via%20Getty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b85bf3a96e437d6eb865a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Rober%20is%20among%20several%20top%20YouTube%20creators%20who%20have%20found%20a%20new%20home%20on%20Netflix.%3Cp%3E%3A%20Noam%20Galai%2FNBC%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENetflix's%20co-CEO%20said%20the%20streamer%20boosted%20YouTuber%20Mark%20Rober's%20product%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETed%20Sarandos%20said%20that%20Netflix's%20podcast%20and%20creator%20content%20push%20is%20showing%20promise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20the%20model%20for%20talk%20shows%20has%20changed%20with%20the%20decline%20of%20large%20broadcast%20TV%20audiences.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-history-streaming-growth-story-hollywood-disruption-subscribers-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%3C%2Fa%3E%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20says%20the%20streamer's%20push%20into%20podcasting%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutube-netflix-fox-changing-nature-of-podcasts-tv-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EYouTube-born%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20bearing%20fruit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarandos%20specifically%20called%20out%20science%20educator%20Mark%20Rober's%20show%20as%20an%20early%20success.%20He%20stressed%20that%20Netflix%20was%20both%20allowing%20the%20YouTube%20star%20to%20reach%20a%20larger%20audience%20and%20also%20sell%20more%20of%20his%20science%20kits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20he%20saw%20was%20a%20big%20increase%20in%20his%20consumer%20product%20sales%20after%20this%20first%20week%20on%20Netflix%2C%20even%20though%20he%20reaches%20an%20enormous%20audience%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said%20in%20a%20new%20interview%20with%20POLITICO%2C%20which%2C%20like%20Business%20Insider%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20%26quot%3BMark%20Rober's%20CrunchLabs%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20launched%20in%20November%2C%20the%20former%20NASA%20engineer%20stages%20science%20experiments%20and%20competitions%20in%20his%20backyard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarandos%20said%20he%20was%20also%20bullish%20on%20Netflix's%20Pete%20Davidson%20interview%20show%2C%20as%20well%20as%20its%20official%20behind-the-scenes%20podcasts%20about%20popular%20shows%20like%20%26quot%3BBridgerton.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20video%20podcast%20is%20just%20the%20evolution%20of%20talk%20shows%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYouTube%2C%20already%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreators-reshaping-hollywood-youtube-netflix-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etop%20US%20streaming%20TV%20service%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20has%20solidified%20its%20position%20as%20the%20No.%201%20destination%20for%20podcasts.%20Netflix%20has%20been%20looking%20to%20challenge%20YouTube%20by%20luring%20some%20of%20its%20star%20creators%20like%20Rober%20and%20preschool%20educator%20Ms.%20Rachel.%20Netflix%20also%20rolled%20out%20a%20slate%20of%20video%20podcasts%20early%20this%20year%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-stream-bill-simmons-other-popular-video-podcasts-spotify-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBill%20Simmons'%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%2C%20Charlamagne%20Tha%20God's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Breakfast%20Club%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20Barstool%20Sports%20fare.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20creator%20reps%20have%20wondered%20whether%20Netflix%20can%20turn%20its%20viewers%20into%20habitual%20consumers%20of%20video%20podcasts%2C%20and%20whether%20leaving%20YouTube%20will%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-video-podcast-push-shows-to-challenge-youtube-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecost%20creators%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20audience%20and%20revenue.%20Netflix%20has%20sought%20video%20exclusivity%20with%20many%20of%20its%20podcast%20deals%2C%20while%20some%20YouTube%20creators'%20deals%2C%20like%20Rober's%20and%20Ms.%20Rachel's%2C%20have%20been%20nonexclusive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarandos%20said%20Netflix%20was%20seeing%20%26quot%3Bpromising%20numbers%26quot%3B%20from%20its%20podcasts%2C%20which%20focus%20on%20subjects%20like%20comedy%2C%20sports%2C%20and%20true%20crime%2C%20areas%20that%20already%20do%20well%20on%20the%20platform.%20He%20didn't%20share%20specific%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20broadcast%20TV%20audiences%20have%20shrunk%2C%20viewership%20for%20traditional%20talk%20shows%20has%20declined%2C%20and%20Sarandos%20acknowledged%20the%20difficulty%20of%20porting%20the%20format%20to%20streaming%20services.%20Netflix%20has%20had%20some%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-eyeing-video-podcasts-creators-next-growth-act-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egrowing%20pains%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20talk%20shows%2C%20which%20often%20haven't%20drawn%20huge%20audiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20tried%20to%20and%20failed%20at%20many%20talk%20shows%20over%20the%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said.%20%26quot%3BMuch%20smaller%20audiences%20tune%20into%20multiple%20shows%20in%20the%20form%20of%20a%20podcast%20every%20day.%20It's%20a%20deeper%20relationship%20than%20it%20is%20a%20broad%20one.%20So%2C%20instead%20of%20trying%20to%20make%20one%20show%20for%20the%20world%2C%20you%20might%20have%20to%20make%20hundreds%20or%20thousands%20of%20shows%20for%20the%20whole%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-mark-rober-product-sales-boosted-by-netflix-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773730801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b85bf3a96e437d6eb865a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-mark-rober-product-sales-boosted-by-netflix-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20says%20the%20streamer's%20push%20into%20podcasting%20and%20YouTube-born%20content%20is%20bearing%20fruit.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoutuber-mark-rober-product-sales-boosted-by-netflix-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gas%20on%20the%20line%3A%20will%20the%20Iran%20war%20squeeze%20India's%20piped%20gas%20next%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773730062000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2Fa248%2Flive%2Fca970430-21c3-11f1-a79a-77e93010d956.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcj6dl175w01o%230%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Iran%20war%20has%20already%20rattled%20LPG%20users.%20Will%20India%E2%80%99s%20piped%20gas%20network%20face%20the%2