hat%20he%20proposed%20instead.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22President%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Netflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b85a69a7a4f9df67ba6b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Netflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%3Cp%3EHeather%20Diehl%2FAndrew%20Leyden%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ENetflix's%20co-CEO%20said%20he's%20asked%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20avoid%20tariffs%20on%20foreign-made%20films%20and%20TV.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETed%20Sarandos%20said%20he%20thinks%20tax%20incentives%20are%20a%20better%20bet%20to%20boost%20US%20production.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGlobal%20filmmaking%20has%20been%20a%20key%20differentiator%20for%20Netflix%20in%20the%20streaming%20wars.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENetflix%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20doesn't%20think%20tariffs%20are%20the%20right%20way%20to%20boost%20US%20movie%20and%20TV%20production%20%E2%80%94%20and%20he%20thinks%20he's%20gotten%20through%20to%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20has%20brought%20up%20tariffs%20for%20the%20movie%20and%20television%20industry%20many%20times%2C%20and%20I've%20hopefully%20talked%20to%20him%20the%20way%20out%20of%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20said%20in%20a%20new%20interview%20with%20POLITICO%2C%20which%2C%20alongside%20Business%20Insider%2C%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Axel%20Springer%20Global%20Reporters%20Network.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20been%20keen%20on%20using%20tariffs%20to%20encourage%20more%20filming%20in%20the%20US.%20In%20May%2C%20he%20announced%20on%20Truth%20Social%20a%20plan%20to%20impose%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-movie-tariff-plan-baffles-hollywood-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E100%25%20tariff%20on%20films%3C%2Fa%3E%20produced%20outside%20the%20US.%20He%20hasn't%20implemented%20it%20so%20far.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20plan%20to%20add%20tariffs%20on%20foreign%20movies%20stemmed%20from%20a%20desire%20to%20slow%20production%20declines%20in%20Hollywood%20and%20other%20areas%20of%20the%20US%20that%20%26quot%3Bare%20being%20devastated%26quot%3B%20by%20filming%20incentive%20programs%20abroad%2C%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20May%20announcement%20on%20Truth%20Social.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-leaving-los-angeles-remote-work-tv-movies-money-streaming-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELos%20Angeles%20production%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20dropping%20off%20for%20years%2C%20and%20the%20city's%20media%20professionals%20are%20feeling%20the%20pain.%20Overseas%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hollywoodreporter.com%2Fbusiness%2Fbusiness-news%2Flondon-new-hollywood-1236208885%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efilming%20hubs%20like%20London%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20courting%20production%20work%20by%20offering%20big%20cost-saving%20incentives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESarandos%20said%20he'd%20prefer%20the%20US%20use%20similar%20tax%20incentives%20to%20bring%20filming%20back%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHealthy%20incentive%20programs%20attract%20a%20lot%20of%20production%2C%20and%20you've%20seen%20a%20lot%20of%20them%20move%20from%20California%20to%20Georgia%20to%20New%20Jersey%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarandos%20told%20POLITICO.%20%26quot%3BHaving%20the%20incentives%20versus%20tariffs%20is%20much%20better.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20tariff%20structure%20for%20a%20movie%2C%20which%20isn't%20a%20physical%20good%2C%20isn't%20entirely%20clear.%20A%20White%20House%20spokesman%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20shortly%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhollywood-trump-tariffs-movie-tv-winners-losers-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETrump's%20announcement%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%26quot%3Bno%20final%20decisions%20on%20foreign%20film%20tariffs%26quot%3B%20had%20been%20made%20and%20that%20the%20administration%20was%20%26quot%3Bexploring%20all%20options%20to%20deliver%20on%20President%20Trump's%20directive%20to%20safeguard%20our%20country's%20national%20and%20economic%20security%20while%20Making%20Hollywood%20Great%20Again.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20fee%20on%20foreign%20productions%20could%20become%20very%20expensive%20for%20Netflix%2C%20which%20has%20released%20a%20slate%20of%20international%20films%20and%20TV%20shows%20over%20the%20years%2C%20including%20%26quot%3BAll%20Quiet%20on%20the%20Western%20Front%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSquid%20Game%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAdolescence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finternational-producers-netflix-disney-rise-of-global-tv-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix's%20global%20reach%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20its%20ability%20to%20turn%20a%20South%20Korean%20or%20German%20drama%20into%20a%20global%20hit%20have%20been%20key%20differentiators%20for%20the%20company%2C%20which%20is%20expected%20to%20spend%20as%20much%20as%20%2420%20billion%20on%20content%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-sarandos-netflix-asked-trump-to-back-off-movie-tariffs-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773727201000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b85a69a7a4f9df67ba6b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fted-sarandos-netflix-asked-trump-to-back-off-movie-tariffs-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Netflix's%20co-CEO%20Ted%20Sarandos%20said%20he%20advised%20Trump%20to%20avoid%20tariffs%20on%20foreign-made%20movies.%20He%20pushed%20instead%20for%20tax%20incentives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22dwhateley%40businessinsider.com%20(Dan%20Whateley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2